## Deva World

p:Welcome,

p:You have entered the realm of the Deva. A virtual reality created from the ancient texts of the Rig Veda with some modern flair.
p:The realm of the Deva is a rich adventure into your imagination where you will find places like...
> Vedic Law Library
> Houses of the Deities
> Arjika Military
> Arjika Akademy
> Offering Halls
> Adventure Arcade
> 1977 Disneyland
> Much More...
